Data Partitioning:


AWS Dynamo:
- Has a out-pf-the-box feature to handle spikes / hot-partition problem. It moves the data from 1 node to another to ensure load is balanced.
- Similar tool Shopify created, which helps in moving data of a shop tp another DB node to balance load/query

